snippet.title: Best VGM 735 - Dragon Quest IX - Heaven's Prayer (The Observatory)
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 2154 - https://youtu.be/xP3PDznPrw4

Symphonic Suite version here: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mowxn3woS50

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo DS
Dragon Quest IX : Sentinels of the Starry Skies (2009)
The Observatory (天使界)
Koichi Sugiyama
